title: Sir Croaksalot
description: A noble frog knight who guards the lily pad kingdom with his mighty ribbit. Beware his Croak of Justice!

title: Hoppy Potter
description: The frog who lived... to leap! Master of amphibious magic and potions that bubble like a bog.

title: The Ribbitron
description: Part frog, part machine, all ribbit. Programmed to hop nonstop and compute the perfect fly-catching trajectory.

title: Professor Croakins
description: The wisest frog in the pond. Known for his lectures on 'Advanced Fly-ology' and 'The Art of the Hop.'

title: Fly-Swatter
description: This frog has one job, and he does it well. No fly is safe when Fred is on the hunt!

title: Frogzilla
description: A giant among frogs, Frogzilla terrorizes small ponds everywhere. Legend says he once ate a fly the size of a hummingbird.

title: Toadally Groovy
description: This groovy frog is all about good vibes and high hops. Known for his radical lily pad surfing skills.

title: Croak and Dagger
description: A mysterious, shadowy frog that appears out of nowhere. Specialized in stealthy croaks and silent leaps.
